Detect persistence and privilege escalation (HIDS)

OSSEC alerting on adding a new user to the system and escalating privilege comes as an Out-Of-Box rule. You don't have to configure or edit anything within the configuration to see this reflected as alerts.

Open your terminal and execute the following commands in sequence:

  • sudo su
  • useradd attacker
  • su attacker
